-- French National Working for SPIE Killed in Yemen Shooting, Government Says
-- B y   S t e v e   R h i n d s
-- 2010-10-06T09:12:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-06/french-national-working-for-spie-killed-in-yemen-shooting-government-says.html
France’s foreign ministry confirmed
the killing of a French national working for SPIE in Yemen.  The man was shot, according to an e-mailed statement from
the ministry. It didn’t give further details.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steve Rhinds at 
 srhinds@bloomberg.net  